| No rate limiting | High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| Hardcoded port | Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| No body size limit | Medium | Set `limit` in `express.json()` |
| No input validation | High (for future routes) | Use `zod` or `joi` |

