| No rate limiting | 🔴 High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No global error handler | 🟠 Medium | Add error middleware |
| Sensitive data exposure | 🟠 Medium | Restrict `/users` fields |
| No CORS policy | 🟠 Medium | Configure `cors` |
| No 404 handler | 🟡 Low | Add catch-all middleware |
| Hardcoded port | 🟡 Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
