| Area | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| **HTTP Headers** | No security headers | Add `helmet` middleware |
| **Rate Limiting** | Unprotected endpoints | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| **Body Parsing** | Missing middleware | `express.json()` with size limit |
| **Error Handling** | No global error handler | 4-arg error middleware, hides details in production |
| **404 Handling** | Falls through to Express default | Explicit 404 JSON handler |
| **Network Binding** | Binds to `0.0.0.0` | Bind to `127.0.0.1` (or configurable via env) |
| **Graceful Shutdown** | No `SIGTERM` handling | Clean server close on shutdown |
| **Configuration** | Hardcoded port | `PORT`/`HOST` from environment variables |

